author: cbs8
title: U-Haul Moves into High Point
text:
U-Haul
HIGH POINT, N.C. , Sept. 4, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- U-Haul Company of Central North Carolina is pleased to welcome U-Haul Moving and Storage of South Side to its growing network of stores. This U-Haul store will meet the moving needs of the greater High Point community.
Constructed in 1970, this building features 64,612 square feet of space situated on 16.07 acres of land. The facility, located at 1100 Trinity Avenue, was the former home of High Point Home Furnishings Center. With convenient highway access, U-Haul Moving and Storage of South Side is ready to help High Point residents with their truck and trailer rentals .
"This U-Haul store is the most recent addition to the area," explained Connor Royals , general manager. "Our entire team has banded together to make sure that we are serving central North Carolina in the best way possible."
"We pride ourselves on being able to provide a better and better product and service to more and more people, at a lower and lower cost," Royals continued. "It is our goal to be a landmark for both U-Haul Company and the city of High Point ."
The acquisition of High Point Home Furnishings Center was driven by U-Haul Company's Corporate Sustainability initiatives : U-Haul supports infill development to help local communities lower their carbon footprint. Our adaptive reuse of existing buildings reduces the amount of energy and resources required for new-construction materials and helps cities reduce their unwanted inventory of unused buildings.
Visit U-Haul Moving and Storage of South Side for all your moving and storage needs or call (336) 822-9549, Mon. – Thurs. 7 a.m. – 7 p.m. , Fri. 7 a.m. – 8 p.m. , Sat. 7 a.m. – 7 p.m. and Sun. 9 a.m. – 5 p.m. Visit us online at uhaul.com or contact U-Haul Reservations, at 1-800-GO-UHAUL.
To learn more about U-Haul in the news, visit My U-Haul Story .
